RAD_DATASOURCES.DEFAULT_WHERE: PRODUCT_TYPE = 'L' AND MODULE_CODE ='OL' AND CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A','Y')

RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO LINKED_TO_REF, A.BRANCH LINKED_TO_BRANCH, A.CONTRACT_CCY CONTRACT_CCY, B.FACILITY_NAME FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER B WHERE A.PRODUCT_TYPE ='C' AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS = 'A' AND A.AUTH_STATUS = 'A' AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND A.LATEST_VERSION_NO = B.VERSION_NO AND B.VALUE_DATE <= ? AND NVL(NVL(B.LAST_AVAILABLE_DATE,B.MATURITY_DATE),'31-DEC-75') >= NVL(?,'31-DEC-75') AND A.COUNTERPARTY = ? AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO NOT IN (SELECT NVL(LINKED_TO_REF,'X') FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_LINK_AMENDMENT WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND VERSION_NO = (SELECT MAX(VERSION_NO) FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT_LINK_AMENDMENT WHERE CONTRACT_REF_NO = ? AND VERSION_NO < ?)) ORDER BY A.CONTRACT_REF_NO

SELECT A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, A.BRANCH, A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.BOOK_DATE FROM OLTBS_CONTRACT A, OLTBS_CONTRACT_MASTER B, OLTBS_CONTRACT_EVENT_LOG C WHERE A.PRODUCT_TYPE = 'L' AND A.CONTRACT_STATUS IN ('A', 'Y') AND A.CONTRACT_REF_NO = B.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND B.CONTRACT_REF_NO = C.CONTRACT_REF_NO AND A.MODULE_CODE = 'OL' AND A.BRANCH = GLOBAL.CURRENT_BRANCH GROUP BY A.CONTRACT_REF_NO, A.BRANCH, A.PRODUCT_CODE, A.BOOK_DATE ORDER BY A.BOOK_DATE, A.CONTRACT_REF_NO
